description: This is a market on whether the average Ethereum gas price will be below 150 Gwei on May 4, 2021. This market will resolve to "Yes" if the daily average Ethereum gas price is listed as being below 150 Gwei for that date, on Etherscan. If the daily average Ethereum gas price is 150 Gwei or higher for that date, this market will resolve to "No". The resolution source for this market is https://etherscan.io/chart/gasprice. This market will resolve when data is available for the date of May 4, 2021. In the event of ambiguity in terms of the market outcome, the market will be resolved at the sole discretion of the Markets Integrity Committee (MIC).
